  optional xf86-input-elo2300     '' '' for input device
  optional xf86-input-elographics '' '' for input device
  optional xf86-input-evdev       '' '' for input device
  optional xf86-input-fpit        '' '' for input device
  optional xf86-input-hyperpen    '' '' for input device
  optional xf86-input-jamstudio   '' '' for input device
  optional xf86-input-joystick    '' '' for input device
  optional xf86-input-keyboard    '' '' for input device
  optional xf86-input-magellan    '' '' for input device
